&lt;h1 id="alien-truth"&gt;Alien Truth&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;October 2022&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If there were intelligent beings elsewhere in the universe, they&amp;rsquo;d share certain truths in common with us. The truths of mathematics would be the same, because they&amp;rsquo;re true by definition. Ditto for the truths of physics; the mass of a carbon atom would be the same on their planet. But I think we&amp;rsquo;d share other truths with aliens besides the truths of math and physics, and that it would be worthwhile to think about what these might be.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Aliens Would Visit for Knowledge, Not Resources</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/aliens-would-visit-for-knowledge-not-resources/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 20:17:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/aliens-would-visit-for-knowledge-not-resources/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/aliens-would-visit-for-knowledge-not-resources.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
