&lt;p&gt;The universe should be teeming with aliens&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
Let’s talk briefly about the Fermi paradox since we’re talking about aliens. For listeners who don’t know, Enrico Fermi was a famous physicist who was part of the Manhattan Project. He said, &amp;ldquo;Where are the aliens?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>It’s Mind Blowing That Our Minds Can’t Be Blown</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Oct 2021 18:42:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
